            <div class="sg-card-cell">
              <div class="pi-card">
                <p class="pi-eyebrow">Card standard</p>
                <h3 style="font-size: var(--ty-h3-prose); margin: 8px 0;">Titolo esempio</h3>
                <p style="font-size: var(--ty-meta); color: var(--pianeta-muted-strong); margin: 0;">Radius 18 · pad 22 · bg card · border default.</p>
              </div>
              <code class="sg-swatch-name">.pi-card</code>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<div class="pi-card">...</div>'}</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="sg-card-cell">
              <div class="pi-card pi-card--sm">
                <p class="pi-eyebrow">Card small</p>
                <h3 style="font-size: var(--ty-h3-prose); margin: 8px 0;">Titolo esempio</h3>
                <p style="font-size: var(--ty-meta); color: var(--pianeta-muted-strong); margin: 0;">Radius 14 · pad 18.</p>
              </div>
              <code class="sg-swatch-name">.pi-card.pi-card--sm</code>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<div class="pi-card pi-card--sm">...</div>'}</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="sg-card-cell">
              <div class="sg-method-card">
                <span class="sg-method-n">01</span>
                <strong>Discovery</strong>
                <p>Il metodo di <code>/hire</code>: chip arancio in cima, titolo bold, descrizione muted.</p>
              </div>
              <code class="sg-swatch-name">.method-card (HireLanding)</code>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<div class="method-card"><span class="method-n">01</span>...</div>'}</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="sg-card-cell">
              <div class="sg-offer-card" style="border-top: 3px solid var(--cta-primary);">
                <div class="sg-offer-price">Da progetto</div>
                <h3 class="sg-offer-name">✳️ Foundation</h3>
                <p class="sg-offer-forwho">Per team che partono da zero.</p>
                <ul class="sg-offer-bullets"><li>✓ Design system</li><li>✓ Landing</li><li>✓ Delivery</li></ul>
                <span class="sg-offer-link" style="color: var(--cta-primary);">Scopri →</span>
              </div>
              <code class="sg-swatch-name">.offer-card (HireLanding)</code>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<a class="offer-card" style="border-top:3px solid …">...</a>'}</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="sg-card-cell">
              <div class="pi-card" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--cta-primary);">
                <blockquote style="font-size: var(--ty-quote); line-height: var(--ty-quote-lh); margin: 0;">
                  “Standard aperti. Codice consegnato.”
                </blockquote>
                <p style="font-size: var(--ty-meta); color: var(--pianeta-muted); margin: 12px 0 0;">— Manifesto Pianeta</p>
              </div>
              <code class="sg-swatch-name">Quote card (composita)</code>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<div class="pi-card"><blockquote>…</blockquote></div>'}</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- OVERLAYS -->
        <section id="overlays" class="th-section th-subsection">
          <h2 class="pi-h2">Overlays & Chrome</h2>
          <p class="th-lead">Elementi di chrome del sito — descrizione + snippet. Nessuna demo interattiva qui (per non rompere lo stato della pagina).</p>

          <div class="sg-overlay-list">
            <article class="pi-card">
              <h3 class="sg-h3">SiteRail</h3>
              <p class="th-lead">Rail laterale sinistro (60px), trasparente. Contiene logo Pianeta, eyebrow contestuale, theme switcher (Light/Auto/Dark), locale switcher IT/EN. Persiste su tutte le pagine con <code>chrome=true</code>.</p>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<SiteRail current={Astro.url.pathname} />'}</code></pre>
            </article>

            <article class="pi-card">
              <h3 class="sg-h3">Detail overlay (.work-ov-panel)</h3>
              <p class="th-lead">Pannello laterale che scorre da destra su click da index pages (work, bulletin, services). Contiene detail-head + detail-hero + detail-body. Chiude con ESC o click fuori.</p>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<div class="work-ov-panel">…</div>'}</code></pre>
            </article>

            <article class="pi-card">
              <h3 class="sg-h3">Team overlay (.team-ov-panel)</h3>
              <p class="th-lead">Variante del detail overlay per pagine team — con foto profilo, ruolo, bio breve, link a progetti.</p>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<div class="team-ov-panel">…</div>'}</code></pre>
            </article>

            <article class="pi-card">
              <h3 class="sg-h3">NewsletterPopup</h3>
              <p class="th-lead">Popup proattivo con iscrizione alla Bulletin (audience Resend). Nascosto qui via <code>hideNewsletter=true</code>. Anche AlbaProactivePopup segue lo stesso flag.</p>
              <pre class="sg-code"><code>{'<BaseLayout hideNewsletter={true}>'}</code></pre>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- UTILITY CLASSES -->
        <section id="utility" class="th-section th-subsection">
          <h2 class="pi-h2">Utility classes <code>.pi-*</code></h2>
          <p class="th-lead">Prefisso <code>.pi-*</code> — sistema unico condiviso da tutte le pagine.</p>
          <div class="sg-util-grid">
            {utilityClasses.map((u) => (
              <div class="sg-util-row">
                <code class="sg-swatch-name">{u.cls}</code>
                <span class="pi-meta-value">{u.desc}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- DARK MODE -->
        <section id="dark" class="th-section th-subsection">
          <h2 class="pi-h2">Dark mode</h2>
          <p class="th-lead">Attivata via <code>data-theme="dark"</code> (o <code>data-theme="auto"</code> + <code>data-sun="night"</code>). Testa qui col toggle in cima alla pagina.</p>

          <div class="sg-dark-table">
              <div class="sg-dark-row sg-dark-head">
                <span>Cosa cambia</span>
                <span>Come lo garantisci</span>
              </div>
              <div class="sg-dark-row">
                <span>Background surface</span>
                <span><code>--pianeta-bg-card</code> passa da <code>#ffffff</code> → <code>#1a1d23</code>. Usa <code>.pi-card</code> o <code>var(--pianeta-bg-card)</code>, mai <code>#fff</code> hard-coded.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="sg-dark-row">
                <span>Text</span>
                <span><code>--pianeta-text</code> passa da <code>#0e1116</code> → <code>#f5f4ee</code>. Non usare mai il valore hex diretto.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="sg-dark-row">
                <span>Muted</span>
                <span><code>--pianeta-muted</code> passa a <code>rgba(245,244,238,0.58)</code>. Le rgba <code>(14,17,22,.xx)</code> vanno tokenizzate.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="sg-dark-row">
                <span>Border</span>
                <span><code>--pianeta-border</code> flippa colore base (bianco su nero). Le border card lo usano già.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="sg-dark-row">
                <span>CTA secondary</span>
                <span><code>--cta-secondary</code> <code>#1f5b8f</code> → <code>#4a8fc4</code> (contrast preservato su bg scuro).</span>
              </div>
              <div class="sg-dark-row">
                <span>--soft</span>
                <span><code>#f3f2ea</code> → <code>#15181e</code>. Le sezioni <code>.pi-sec-soft</code> restano distinte dal background principale.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="sg-dark-row">
                <span>--band</span>
                <span>Resta <code>#14171c</code> in entrambi i temi (design intenzionale).</span>
              </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- META -->
        <section id="meta" class="th-section">
          <h2 class="pi-h2">Update meta</h2>
          <div class="pi-card meta-card">
            <p class="meta">
              <strong>Ultimo aggiornamento (build):</strong> {now}<br />
              <strong>Fonte dei dati:</strong> build-time filesystem scan (<code>import.meta.glob</code> +
              <code>getCollection</code>). Ogni deploy re-esegue lo scan e riflette lo stato reale del repo.
              I valori dei token sono risolti client-side con <code>getComputedStyle</code>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- ANCHOR NAV STICKY -->
      <aside class="th-aside">
        <p class="pi-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Indice</p>
        <nav class="th-anchors" aria-label="Indice sezioni">
          {sections.map((s) => (
            <a href={`#${s.id}`} data-anchor={s.id} class={`th-anchor${s.label.startsWith('· ') ? ' th-anchor-sub' : ''}`}>
              {s.label}
            </a>
          ))}
        </nav>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Nascondi la CTA fissa "Lavoriamo insieme" su questa pagina interna */
  :global(.hub-hire-cta) { display: none !important; }

  .th-root { padding-top: 40px; padding-bottom: 96px; }

  .th-hero { text-align: left; padding-top: 32px; padding-bottom: 32px; }
  .th-hero .pi-hero-sub { margin-top: 14px; max-width: 68ch; }
  .th-hero code { background: var(--soft); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85em; }

  .th-toolbar { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; align-items: center; margin-top: 28px; padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--soft); border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--pianeta-border); }
  .th-theme { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .th-theme-btns { display: inline-flex; gap: 4px; padding: 4px; background: var(--pianeta-bg-card); border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid var(--pianeta-border); }
  .th-theme-btn { border: 0; background: transparent; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; color: var(--pianeta-muted-strong); }
  .th-theme-btn[data-active="true"] { background: var(--cta-primary); color: var(--cta-primary-ink); }
  .th-hint { margin: 0; }

  .th-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; margin-top: 32px; }
  @media (min-width: 960px) {
    .th-layout { grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 240px; align-items: start; gap: 64px; }
  }

  .th-aside { order: -1; }
  @media (min-width: 960px) {
    .th-aside { order: 1; position: sticky; top: 24px; max-height: calc(100vh - 48px); overflow-y: auto; }
  }

  .th-anchors { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .th-anchor { display: block; padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--pianeta-muted-strong); font-size: 13.5px; transition: background 150ms, color 150ms; }
  .th-anchor:hover { background: var(--soft); color: var(--pianeta-text); }
  .th-anchor[data-current="true"] { background: var(--soft); color: var(--pianeta-text); font-weight: 600; }
  .th-anchor-sub { padding-left: 22px; font-size: 12.5px; }

  .th-section { padding: 48px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--pianeta-border); scroll-margin-top: 24px; }
  .th-section:first-of-type { border-top: 0; padding-top: 0; }
  .th-subsection { padding: 32px 0; }
  .th-section h2 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .th-lead { color: var(--pianeta-muted-strong); font-size: var(--ty-meta); line-height: 1.6; margin: 8px 0 24px; max-width: 68ch; }
  .th-lead code { background: var(--soft); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; }

  /* Overview stats */
  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin: 8px 0 0; }
  .stat { background: var(--pianeta-bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--pianeta-border); border-radius: var(--radius-card-sm); padding: 16px 18px; }
  .stat-n { font: var(--ty-h2-sec); color: var(--pianeta-text); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .stat-l { font: var(--ty-meta); color: var(--pianeta-muted); }

  /* Tabelle mappa */
  .tbl { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font: var(--ty-body); }
  .tbl th, .tbl td { text-align: left; padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--pianeta-border); vertical-align: top; }
  .tbl th { font: var(--ty-meta); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--pianeta-muted); background: transparent; }
  .tbl tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .tbl .c { text-align: center; width: 60px; }
  .tbl .meta { font: var(--ty-meta); color: var(--pianeta-muted); }
  .ok { color: var(--cta-primary); font-weight: 600; }
  .ko { color: var(--pianeta-muted); }

  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .h3 { font: var(--ty-h3-prose); color: var(--pianeta-text); margin: 0 0 12px; }
  .dl { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr; gap: 6px 12px; margin: 0; font: var(--ty-body); }
  .dl dt { font: var(--ty-meta); color: var(--pianeta-muted); }
  .dl dd { margin: 0; }

  .bar { display: inline-block; width: 100px; height: 6px; background: var(--pianeta-border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px; }
  .bar-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--cta-primary); border-radius: 4px; }

  .meta-card { background: var(--soft); }

  code { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 0.92em; color: var(--pianeta-text); }

  /* ==== Design tokens sections (styleguide styles) ==== */
  .sg-h3 { font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--pianeta-muted-strong); margin: 32px 0 16px; }

  /* Colors */
  .sg-color-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
